Help: classes
 There are several classes in this game.
 You get to choose one in the beginnnig.
 Class can not be changed in game.
List of all classes and their features:
  warior  - gets damage from strength
  thief   - gets damage from agility
  magus   - gets damage from intelect
  ranger  - gets reduced damage from strength and agility
  paladin - gets reduced damage from strength and intelect
  warmage - gets reduced damage from intelect and agility
  guru    - gets highly reduced damage from strength, agility and intelect
